title: #199 - Moonshine, Trae Crowder, Corey Forrester, Drew Morgan, & ME
description: Comedians Trae Crowder, Corey Forrester, & Drew Morgan hang with me in the Mancave, drink Moonshine, & talk about Trae's viral videos The Liberal Redneck, their new Book The Liberal Redneck Manifesto, the south, racism, & Speedos!!!
